== Welcome to the Apoidea Project ==

Secure and anonymous file sharing in Erlang.
Made by The Awesome Team at Uppsala University.

Sunshine!

PREREQUISITES:
	1. Erlang
	2. EUnit
	3. EDoc
	4. GNU Make
	
DOWNLOAD:
	After you have created an account on GitHub you can run
	$ git clone git@github.com:ephracis/Apoidea.git
	
BUILD AND RUN:
	$ cd Apoidea
	$ make
	$ make start_drone
	
	Open up a second terminal and run:
	$ make start_uploader
	
	Open up a third terminal and run:
	$ make start_downloader
	
	Shut down the drone with Ctrl-C afterwards
	
FURTHER INSTRUCTIONS:
	$ make help
